OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"(We) had no understanding of what
OL,8,FSUDEP was. We knew she had severe
OL,9,Fepilepsy, but we didn't think it was a
OL,10,Flife or death situation".
OL,12,FAlison explained "If somebody had said
OL,13,Fto us '1 in 100' we would have done
OL,14,Fanything we could have to support
OL,15,Fher... that information should have
OL,16,Fbeen shared to us...".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@BpmoD@EpnrD@XO]tD@ROUxD@UO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe family say they would have
OL,8,Fimplemented measures to protect Megan,
OL,9,Fsuch as 24 hour monitoring, alarms,
OL,10,Fand lifestyle changes, had they been
OL,11,Faware of the risk.
OL,13,FShe believes that Megan may still be
OL,14,Falive "if only she had been given the
OL,15,Fright opportunities, the right support
OL,16,Fand the right care."
OL,18,F"I wanted to support her to be a mum,
OL,19,Fbut it was more important we have a
OL,20,FMegan."
OL,26,@vD@GOUxD@TO]zD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
