FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAn inquest into Megan's death
OL,8,Fconcluded in May. It was the first in
OL,9,FWales to address the importance of
OL,10,FSUDEP risk discussions in epilepsy
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FThe Coroner found that there was no
OL,14,Fdocumented confirmation that Megan's
OL,15,Fhigh risk of SUDEP was discussed with
OL,16,Fher, nor was there any discussion of
OL,17,Fwider protective measures up until
OL,18,FApril 2022. She found that even after
OL,19,Fthat date, there was no individualised
OL,20,Frisk discussion with Megan.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe Coroner also identified two missed
OL,8,Fopportunities for discussions about
OL,9,Frisks and preventative measures prior
OL,10,Fto her death.
OL,12,FThe Coroner has now requested a
OL,13,Ffurther statement from the Health
OL,14,FBoard setting out how SUDEP risk is
OL,15,Fdiscussed with patients and how
OL,16,Fpatients' individual risks are
OL,17,Fsufficiently considered and addressed.
OL,19,FAlison welcomes this outcome, and says
OL,20,F"what we learnt is what good quality
OL,21,Fcare could have achieved"
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"If you're having these appointments
OL,8,Fit's supposed to be individualised
OL,9,Fcare, not generalised care"
OL,11,F"We know there's nothing that can
OL,12,Fchange what happened, but the hope is
OL,13,Fthat something good can come out of
OL,14,FMegan's death" says Tesni.
OL,16,F"We want justice for her."
OL,18,FIn response, Cardiff and Vale
OL,19,FUniversity Health Board said:
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@[O]sD@AOUvD@NO]xD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
