PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1782308901
OL,3,C'Health board failed our pregnant
OL,4,Cdaughter' says family after epilepsy
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"We remain committed to listening to
OL,8,Fthe experiences of patients and
OL,9,Ffamilies and to learning wherever
OL,10,Fimprovements can be made. We have
OL,11,Fpreviously offered to meet with
OL,12,FMegan's family to discuss their
OL,13,Fconcerns and this offer remains open."
OL,15,FWatch Y Byd ar Bedwar: Epilepsi -
OL,16,FMarwolaeth Megan on Monday 22nd June,
OL,17,Fon S4C, YouTube, BBC iPlayer and S4C
OL,18,FClic.
